    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_6_657-695",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "657-695",
      "markText": "道德的政治如果不以不可磨灭的人类感情为基础的话，就别想建立起任何持久的优势。",
      "totalCount": 1224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=657&rangeEnd=695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=657&rangeEnd=695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_5_862-900",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "862-900",
      "markText": "平庸的头脑不习惯于分析事物，而习惯于根据传统而不是根据考察来接受强烈的印象。",
      "totalCount": 1133,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=862&rangeEnd=900",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=862&rangeEnd=900"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_5_1084-1138",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1084-1138",
      "markText": "只有极少数的民族不是等待缓慢的人类组合更迭运动在坏的极点上开创好的起端，而是利用优秀的法律促进其中间的过渡。",
      "totalCount": 1056,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1084&rangeEnd=1138",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1084&rangeEnd=1138"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_7_844-886",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "844-886",
      "markText": "代表社会的君主只能制定约束一切成员的普遍性法律，但不能判定某个人是否违反了社会契约。",
      "totalCount": 1040,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=844&rangeEnd=886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=844&rangeEnd=886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_19_1729-1821",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1729-1821",
      "markText": "严峻的刑罚造成了这样一种局面：罪犯所面临的恶果越大，也就越敢于逃避刑罚。为了摆脱对一次罪行的刑罚，人们会犯下更多的罪行。刑罚最残酷的国家和年代往往就是行为最血腥、最不人道的国家和年代。",
      "totalCount": 972,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1729&rangeEnd=1821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1729&rangeEnd=1821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_20_4233-4299",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "4233-4299",
      "markText": "体现公共意志的法律憎恶并惩罚谋杀行为，而自己却在做这种事情；它阻止公民去做杀人犯，却安排一个公共的杀人者。我认为这是一种荒谬的现象。",
      "totalCount": 935,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4233&rangeEnd=4299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4233&rangeEnd=4299"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_11_1392-1467",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1392-1467",
      "markText": "优秀的法律应当为主要法官配置一些随机产生的而不是选举产生的陪审官，因为，在这种情况下，根据感情作出判断的无知，较之根据见解作出判断的学识要更可靠一些。",
      "totalCount": 890,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1392&rangeEnd=1467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1392&rangeEnd=1467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_6_858-945",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "858-945",
      "markText": "没有一个人为了公共利益将自己的那份自由毫无代价地捐赠出来，这只是浪漫的空想。只要可能，我们当中的每一个人都希望约束别人的公约不要约束我们自己，都希望成为世界上一切组合的中心。",
      "totalCount": 884,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=858&rangeEnd=945",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=858&rangeEnd=945"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_7_664-710",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "664-710",
      "markText": "只有法律才能为犯罪规定刑罚。只有代表根据社会契约而联合起来的整个社会的立法者才拥有这一权威。",
      "totalCount": 812,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=664&rangeEnd=710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=664&rangeEnd=710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_2_3461-3514",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "3461-3514",
      "markText": "对于一切事物，尤其是艰难的事物，人们不应期待播种与收获同时进行，为了使它们逐渐成熟，必须有一个培育的过程。",
      "totalCount": 770,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24905597&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3461&rangeEnd=3514",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/477329c0717c077d4772152?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3461&rangeEnd=3514"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24905597_19_820-855",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "820-855",
      "markText": "刑罚的目的仅仅在于：阻止罪犯再重新侵害公民，并规诫其他人不要重蹈覆辙。",
